7-28T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2b3b0f79a2a783855e3bfd37d4c11ca3e061b224","tid":1377341,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"【建議】<br />\n推俾樓主<br />\n只要香城主要交通幹道用唔到，就會配合罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n1. 香城紅磡海底隧道<br />\n集合點1:理工大學門口<br />\n集合點2:維多利亞公園銅鑼灣入口噴水池<br />\n<br />\n2. 香城東區海底隧道/東區走廊<br />\n集合點：鰂魚涌公園<br />\n<br />\n3. 香城獅子山隧道<br />\n集合點：浸會大學善衡校園<br />\n<br />\n4. 香城大老山隧道<br />\n集合點：牛池灣公園<br />\n<br />\n預計凌晨開始集合，清晨六點開始行動"},{"pid":"87bbadb2bfba9fde695ea85b5c3b3ba73623152f","tid":1377341,"uid":23198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b54be79693bfb5dfe4fcbb90c00dc4d4c50f4ec3","tid":1377341,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:06:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14c8a2156837b40f9560303aa268b6efc1a183b4","tid":1377341,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，唔該大家真係思考下。<br />\n仲要今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒做少少文宣係關於香港獨立，不過要soft啲係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a08e0031d5f1d2a2fbeb3255dc0752f46554c5","tid":1377341,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd90b9815fd883c61c4368051373289091acf906","tid":1377341,"uid":280209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a2ef37b68516539ab489285de9685710c7499a9b","tid":1377341,"uid":281720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"呢個的確係最有效既方法"},{"pid":"50c6c5f12ac7fc91ea882dafa7b4b9b0a6b175b8","tid":1377341,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5600e97e404de77b94a4790a01afb5b1d1bad594","tid":1377341,"uid":87625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6125ea1638f2aca726ec45e9a7994c96cb5040b","tid":1377341,"uid":87625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3218927cb0288f1b81e7917012d7e97597cc1bff","tid":1377341,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經今日一役 請考慮新抗爭方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/drOhcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/drOhcS</a>"},{"pid":"6e92218d39325193b9bb184a53ec98fefa68a4bf","tid":1377341,"uid":113016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3544b2f51299bec050bbda84dc44225fc3fb807","tid":1377341,"uid":124860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:30:41.000Z","msg":"其實關於罷工我有少少意見<br />\n之前612小弟我都試過膽粗粗射一日波(唔好意思我果時真係唔夠膽直接罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但無論果一日幾嬲都好，都唔敢第二日繼續唔返工<br />\n我諗大部分既人同我都係一樣，好驚只有自己罷工/唔返工，所以點都衝破唔到心理關口<br />\n所以我覺得今次真係要諗方法去「組織」罷工<br />\n有d行業有工會可能會易d，但即使無都好，我地可唔可以係tg group吸引一班同行，係心理上backup一下一班想罷工但又淆底既人?而且有呢d組織先可以長久咁進行罷工，大家有無諗法?"},{"pid":"958ca5a5b5a0d207d59dedd4a2cfe45334b76752","tid":1377341,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0674887a1e008473e908326882af2aa39d9f342d","tid":1377341,"uid":87625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"交通 火車 地鐵 機埸都要停, 公務員都要停<br />\n要政府停擺先係最好方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:32:36.000Z","msg":"8月5日全港齊心大罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n <br />\n齊心一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入黎一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月5號一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae070a32374b25e8c973fe8f3ab028a452c883e","tid":1377341,"uid":268285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"政府地鐵員工一齊罷工，5大訴求，踢走支聯辦港澳辦"}]}